data.description: Delightful Sherman Acres single-level ranch style home in Pleasant Hill enjoys a convenient location and comfortable layout.The living room boasts bright front windows, recessed lighting and fireplace, while the open flow to the dining area features beautiful french doors. The kitchen is well-appointed with white cabinetry, a gas range cooktop, built-in oven & microwave, dining area and an adjacent laundry room with extra storage. The highlight of this home is the oversized family room with glass slider doors leading to a covered back patio and a yard brimming with mature landscaping including fruit trees, a covered patio, lawn area and a large storage shed for all your gardening needs. The spacious primary bedroom enjoys an ensuite bathroom with a walk-in shower. Two additional bedrooms are generously sized, and share a hall bathroom with a shower/tub combo. Located just minutes from downtown Pleasant Hill shopping, dining, the Crossroads shopping center and enjoys easy access to 680 and BART. Whether you're commuting to work or seeking a quiet neighborhood, this home offers the perfect combination of convenience and tranquility. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity!
